      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading paint consistent with its age, while the interior has some visible wear on the upholstery and floor mats. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it may require some minor maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for anyone needing a functional car at a more accessible price point.",
