    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it has been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape\u2014super dependable and runs like a dream! It\u2019s the perfect ride for someone who wants something reliable and well-loved without that brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love how it handles!",
