      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! This car is in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for anyone looking for a reliable set of wheels that still looks great and feels smooth on the road. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
